In re Resignation of Woods.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Woods (1993), 67 Ohio St.3d 1206.]

(No. 93-1780 Submitted September 14, 1993 Decided September 15, 1993.)

The resignation of Thomas Peter Woods of Cincinnati, Ohio, as an attorney, Registration No. 0043226, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., A.W. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright, Resnick and Pfeifer, JJ., concur. F.E. Sweeney, J., dissents.
